          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends title XIX (Medicaid) of the Social Security Act to&nbsp;eliminate restrictions on state Medicaid program coverage of nonprescription drugs for tobacco cessation. Under current law, a state Medicaid program may exclude from coverage, or otherwise restrict, such drugs, except for those&nbsp;recommended to pregnant women.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-01-31T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
